{"tid":219627,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泰爸喺FB直播吊死女兒以報復老婆出軌，然後再上吊自殺身亡","createTime":"2017-04-27T10:42:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T10:53:35.000Z","uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"030da11a09b0fb3a1afa2e0b4578d898a805b682","tid":219627,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:42:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">泰爸直播吊死女兒報復 出軌媽媽崩潰：我想代她死！<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170426/56613818\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170426%2F56613818&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE2owyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=bd6581df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Finternational%2F20170426%2F56613818&h=7669a905\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/international/20170426/56613818</a></div></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170426/large/1493174787_0528.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170426%2Flarge%2F1493174787_0528.jpg&h=a07adacf&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n泰國一名男子與妻子感情觸礁，周一竟利用Facebook Live直播殺死11月大女兒的過程報復，之後自殺，其妻傷心不已，網民都非常心痛。facebook在事後足足一天才刪除片段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，再度捱轟，泰國警方表明會檢討現行移除片段的程序。<br />\n<br />\n「我只能接受女兒已死的事實，我知道時只能希望隨女兒離世，我不想活了，如果可以我希望代替女兒離開。」兇手妻子頌美堤（Jiranuch Triratana）哭着說，場面令人動容。<br />\n<br />\n21歲的威迪訕（Wuttisan Wongtalay）在布吉島國際機場附近一間空置酒店內，直播他將用繩將女兒納塔莉（Natalie）吊死的過程後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，自己再上吊自殺身亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。殺女片段周一下午近5時貼出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，威迪訕的親友見到片段後報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。警方趕到現場後，發現兩人皆已死亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n警方相信威迪訕死前曾與21歲妻子頌美堤爭吵，懷疑妻子不再愛他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，會離他而去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。有報道指，威迪訕不滿妻子紅杏出牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，曾威脅殺死她<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\nFacebook慰問死者家屬，形容事件駭人聽聞。泰國數碼經濟部表示周二下午聯絡fb要求刪片。外電報道，Facebook在案發後約24小時刪除長4分鐘的片段。刪片前片段在YouTube等社交網絡傳播。<br />\n<br />\n美國一名男子上周在Facebook Live播出他當街槍殺一名陌生老翁的片段，fb事隔兩小時才刪片，為人詬病。fb創辦人朱克伯格承諾檢討監察暴力片段及其他具爭議內容的程序。"},{"pid":"c29e802dc5e76f347dbf7028df9c0ef5d9cfe765","tid":219627,"uid":33481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:44:21.000Z","msg":"有無原片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc1896a079811ab70be9d36c379b23b386646d7","tid":219627,"uid":28913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:47:07.000Z","msg":"竟然無人怪條臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69bec6737caf7e2ecdc94c125189a77729d3801b","tid":219627,"uid":24345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:48:54.000Z","msg":"fb變成deep web 越黎越多死亡直播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea3171d4e9f5045edd2f665a18784cc89ee1e8ab","tid":219627,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T10:53:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無原片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有都睇得唔清楚，因為唔係正面睇住個男人點放個BB女出面上吊。"}]}